						<p>East wall of the first <hi rend="italic">prākāra</hi> in the Airāvatēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Rājādhirāja II: Year 12: 1174 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription commences with the <hi rend="italic">praśasti, Kaḍal-śūḻndapārmādarum,</hi> etc., of Rājādhirāja II.</p>						

						<p>It refers to an order <hi rend="italic">(tirumugam)</hi> issued on the 157th day of the 12th year of the king.</p>						

